snippet.title: Northwind - Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description: Northwind is a rogue-lite deck builder monster-hunting game developed by Barking Kitten Interactive. Players will hunt monsters, gather resources, and explore card-making in Northwind Town. Take a look at the latest gameplay trailer for Northwind, launching in 2024 for Linux and PC with a demo available now via Steam.
